						<summary>

						<p>The inscription is highly damaged and is also unfinished. It records some transaction between the temple authorities and certain residents of the village regarding a piece of land brought under cultivation by the latter. The record is assignable to the reign of <hi rend="bold">Uttama-Chōḷa.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
